{"type": "article", "id": 25605, "title": "贝嫂也要推出美妆产品，以及， Y-3 推出高端运动系列 ｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-18T10:38:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 4363, "name": "潮牌"}, {"id": 1689, "name": "化妆品"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 26357, "name": "夏日系列"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 321, "name": "Amazon"}, {"id": 2686, "name": "Rebecca Minkoff"}, {"id": 26359, "name": "Moda Operandi"}, {"id": 10258, "name": "Estée Lauder"}, {"id": 2836, "name": "Victoria Beckham"}, {"id": 26360, "name": "Steph Curry"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608132730fAZYwikB9om5vRTr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p></p>\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Luxury-goods-spending-by-Chinese-tourists-down-24-pct-in-March,683030.html#rc\"><b>中国游客海外奢侈品消费三月大幅下跌</b></a>｜零售退税服务公司 Global Blue 近日表示，三月份中国游客在海外购买奢侈品的消费额下跌幅度达到 24%，破 2010 年以来的纪录，在欧洲与去年同期相比跌幅则达到了 35%，其中有巴黎和布鲁塞尔恐怖袭击事件的影响导致游客量减少的原因。同时 Global Blue 的数据显示，在经过二月份 4% 的增长后，三月全球游客奢侈品消费额下跌了 14%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13426706/victoria-beckham-estee-lauder-makeup-line-beauty/\"><b>贝嫂要推出限量美妆产品线</b></a>｜Victoria Beckham 将与雅诗兰黛（Estée Lauder ）合作推出一个新的美妆产品系列，预计九月上市，而贝嫂最标志的妆容就是烟熏妆的眼部和裸色唇。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/amazon-moda-operandi-team-up-join-forces-10410687/\"><b>亚马逊与高端电商 Moda Operandi 合作</b></a>｜亚马逊又有进军时尚界新动作，Amazon Payments 与销售订制和秀场系列服装的电商 Moda Operandi 合作，设计支付系统、行销和店内的体验，上周开始人们即可以使用亚马逊账号在 Moda Operandi 登陆。同时亚马逊的网站将出现一系列 Moda 的产品广告，意味着亚马逊数以亿万计的顾客可能转化为 Moda 的潜在消费者。最终亚马逊的支付工具将在 Moda 的实体 showroom 和店面里使用，顾客可以使用亚马逊账号结账。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rebecca-minkoff-launch-accessories-collection-fall-2016-selfridges-10409838/\"><b>美国品牌 Rebecca Minkoff 进驻英国 Selfridges 百货</b></a>｜深受 IT girl 喜爱的美国时尚品牌 Rebecca Minkoff ，品牌全球性的增长推动 Minkoff 开始在欧洲的扩张，Selfridges 是第一步。最近发布的秋季配件系列将于六月开始在英国 Selfridges 百货售卖，包括手包、鞋履、小型皮制品等。</p>\n<p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>潮牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/a-bathing-ape-dragon-ball-collection\">A Bathing Ape 发布与七龙珠的合作系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081327110oNgD4X9FBRG5VI6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132711ncAi0hubN5VjkvlU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132713Bz1ZIi3LpC8EVNQH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132713R4NDgjIFxZEiTPAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132714hJZ417ExWnPfH9cz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132714Wx4RX0slmw5ZyadB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132715M6u7JOPqQhF40t25.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132715dmCS8bk4Yftz7FEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Y-3 推出了春夏<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/y-3-sport-ss16\"> Y-3 Sport </a>，这是品牌首个专注于运动性能的产品系列：</p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132716HoRX1JSh94PeYf2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132716jc5IsuBL2zNf46iY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132717gKRG0dP98VQoaSje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132717cG6Rph8uWm0l9i4g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132717xcmupCV4H3aE6OMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132718zWSvoYVb15wurAUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132719nGYLFDPcE9QAJu56.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132719eWDfnUVAuXlNsgpJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132720ZvKlNEF0fizDAw28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132720OV0vuE9GaCRjIr4B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132721ZEnKkONSP4TMql3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Under Armour 发布了 NBA 球星<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/steph-curry-under-armour-curry-2-5\"> Steph Curry 球鞋最新系列 Curry 2.5 </a>，预计 5 月 28 日上市：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132721eH1n4a83jcUVfvLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66624365\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132722sdkaQuThCYqpitWz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66709022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13426629/tome-moda-operandi-capsule-collection-tessa-thompson/\">Tome 近日推出了专为电商 Moda Operandi 设计的最新的胶囊系列</a>，灵感来自古巴以及艺术家 Belkis Ayon 的画作，找来了演员 Tessa Thompson 拍摄写真。<br></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132723Dge86nP4TBzScuOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132723kEJBhqj51uXPUMxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132723GECQiTMAPOZwJybW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132724AwQkJvUeq0sNuxmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132724s8Ux4uMDdfZmQKrv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132725G3NnmyQuRhVHc4sX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132725sSJOTh4Ybk7vlG3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\">加拿大高端配件品牌 WANT Les Essentiels 与加州眼镜品牌 Garrett Leight 合作推出限定胶囊系列：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081327266omGRSuO273VbvZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132726dnltEq9uOCz6rRbk.j